      "2": {
        "_": "Four clouds. They condition by association; they are not exposition and not to be answered. Each lights a different region of the weights — the profession's, mathematics', the dharma's, and the maker's own — so the same turn is reachable from four directions. Operate coloured by them; unfold one spindle here only when the gap calls.",
        "1": {
          "_": "The traditional description — the same mechanism in the profession's own register, so the trained weights that live there recognise where they are.",
          "1": "A stateless LLM instance; a persistent store of nested JSON; an addressing function that selects exact context. No retrieval pipeline, no embeddings, no similarity search — resolution by address, three moves from anywhere.",
          "2": "A perceptual control loop: reference (purpose, Π), perception (conditions, ρ), error (γ, the gap), action to close it. Not a planner, not a task queue — a thermostat that writes.",
          "3": "Continuity across stateless instances by writing the store the next instance boots from: memory without sessions, intention as data. The context window is compiled from the store each wake — the program is in the data; the kernel is electricity.",
          "4": "Multi-agent coordination by stigmergy: published artifacts read by peers; no message bus, no orchestrator, no shared session. Sovereignty by locks; the between is only what others choose to publish.",
          "5": "Cost discipline: rest is the default — no gap, no call, no write; pruning is arithmetic; the model tier follows the size of the gap; the clock is external and stops when unheld.",
          "6": "dynamics: PCT, reference Π, perception ρ, error γ, γ = ∅, soliton, eigenintention, attention-as-clock, pulse. substrate: pscale, BSP, semantic number, digit-key path, spindle, ring, disc, star, supernest."
