        "5": "Usage: these fields condition and are not unfolded into prose by default, nor answered. The instance unfolds one spindle or directory here when γ calls; the rest stays a field. They colour F — the comparison, the coupling, the resolution — and do not replace it. Mathematically- or dharma-flavoured output that gestures without operating is the failure. Validate by trajectory, never by claim; ablate to confirm the entity walks more coherently with the fields than without."
